doctors.name: Dr. kamal Hassan
doctors.bio: Dr. Kamal has over 15 years of experience in pet care and veterinary medicine. He specializes in small animal care and has a special interest in pet nutrition and preventive care.

doctors.name: Dr. Ahmed Ali
doctors.bio: Dr. Ahmed is a skilled veterinary surgeon with 10 years of experience in performing various surgical procedures on pets. He is known for his gentle approach and successful surgical outcomes.

doctors.name: Dr. Mona Samy
doctors.bio: Dr. Mona specializes in diagnosing and treating skin conditions in pets. She has extensive experience in managing allergies, infections, and other dermatological issues in animals.

doctors.name: Dr. Youssef Mahmoud
doctors.qualifications: DVM, Certified in Avian & Exotic Animal Medicine
doctors.bio: With over 12 years of experience, Dr. Youssef specializes in the care of birds, reptiles, and exotic pets. He is passionate about providing specialized care for these unique animals.

doctors.name: Dr. Nada Hossam
doctors.bio: Dr. Nada specializes in animal behavior and training. She helps pet owners understand and modify their pet's behavior using positive reinforcement techniques.

doctors.name: Dr. Omar Hassan
doctors.bio: Specializes in diagnosing and treating common illnesses in small pets such as dogs and cats.

doctors.name: Dr. Ahmed Nabil
doctors.bio: Expert in surgical procedures for pets including orthopedic and soft tissue surgery.

doctors.name: Dr. Khaled Fathy
doctors.bio: Focuses on diagnosing and treating skin diseases and allergies in pets.

doctors.name: Dr. Yasser Samir
doctors.bio: Specialist in dental care and oral surgery for pets.

doctors.name: Dr. Youssef Adel
doctors.bio: Experienced in diagnosing and treating internal diseases in pets.

doctors.name: Dr. Mohamed Sherif
doctors.bio: Helps pet owners with behavior problems and training advice.

doctors.name: Dr. Mahmoud Said
doctors.bio: Specialist in emergency care and critical conditions for pets.

doctors.name: Dr. Nour El-Din
doctors.bio: Provides nutritional plans and advice for pet health and wellness.
